Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:03.00,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Už sme na ceste, Pán Kiril.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.60,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:07.90,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže, zaistite, aby došlo k minimálnemu poškodeniu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:11.40,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Spolieham sa na vás.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:14.31,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetko ide podľa plánu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.90,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To je Album.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:33.49,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Tretí originál.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:53.70,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirytus upokoj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:58.70,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Album na to hovorí?!
