Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.90,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ciel zameraný.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:09.01,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Zahajujem útok.
