Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.50,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Práve ho potvrdzujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.94,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To je Gio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.17,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.22,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Na chrbte Gio je Kamishina Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:45.49,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:48.05,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerá to tak, že prenasleduje Album.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:55.74,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz je už, Spirytus zbytočný.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:57.66,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čata Lindwurm, obnovte sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:17:00.70,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,... Album a Kamishina Jin, sú najvyššia priorita.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:03.04,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:05.01,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci ste ho počuli.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:06.47,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Počuli ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:09.01,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to znamená, že je Spirytus, zbytočný?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:10.87,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To znamená...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.60,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkazy sú jasné.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:18.13,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Howling Star, zabi Spirytusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:21.20,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:22.58,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabiť ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:23.88,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepočul si ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.40,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Howling Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:26.40,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To je rozkaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:29.01,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabi Spirytusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.02,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Štve ma to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:09.70,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj, Toa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:10.89,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To som ja.
