Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:18.02,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo ma opúšťaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.13,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Toa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.73,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Toa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.38,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč mi to, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:19:00.32,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz, keď si videl moju pravú formu, už s tebou nemôžem ostať.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.59,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to hovoríš, Toa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:08.07,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Zbohom, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:12.29,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj, Toa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:23.84,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Toa, zrodil som sa, aby som ta ochraňoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:30.18,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Poďme, Gio.
